$ ansible-playbook install_daart.yml -f 2

PLAY [remote] ******************************************************************

TASK [setup] *******************************************************************
ok: [karst.uits.iu.edu]
ok: [bigred2.uits.iu.edu]

TASK [install DAART] ***********************************************************
changed: [bigred2.uits.iu.edu]
changed: [karst.uits.iu.edu]

PLAY RECAP *********************************************************************
bigred2.uits.iu.edu        : ok=2    changed=1    unreachable=0    failed=0   
karst.uits.iu.edu          : ok=2    changed=1    unreachable=0    failed=0   

